        <p class="featureStory">Lunch is available for purchase through the vendor <a href="http://www.fnlfoods.com/" target="_blank">Fresh n Local</a>, Monday through Friday with hot entrees on Mondays and Fridays and a sack lunch for the remaining weekdays. Milk is included with the purchase of hot lunch and is also available five days a week with the purchase of a milk card. Use the button below to prepay or visit the school office.<br>
