          <h3>Monthly Calendars</h3>
          <p class="featureStory">  Monthly calendars will be coming soon on the Cathedral website. Families are expected to complete and submit the monthly calendar by the 20th of each month. The Facts Tuition Management System is used to collect payments. Monthly charges will be calculated at the end of each month and charged via FACTS on the 5th business day of the following month.</p>
          <h3>Dropoff and Pickup Procedure</h3>
          <p class="featureStory">Parents/guardians must walk students in and sign students in and out daily. Children will not be released to parties, meetings, sports or other activities without prior written authorization from a parent/guardian (signed and dated).</p>
